doc: |
  Souporcell Cluster Overlap

  Build upset plot for clustering results generated by multiple runs of Souporcell


s:about: |
  usage: souporcell_cluster_overlap.R [-h] --clusters CLUSTERS
                                                    [CLUSTERS ...] --aliases
                                                    ALIASES [ALIASES ...]
                                                    [--output OUTPUT]

  Souporcell Cluster Overlap

  options:
    -h, --help            show this help message and exit
    --clusters CLUSTERS [CLUSTERS ...]
                          Path to the Souporcell generated cluster files
    --aliases ALIASES [ALIASES ...]
                          Aliases for cluster files. Order and number of the
                          provided values should correspond to --clusters.
    --output OUTPUT       Output prefix. Default: ./overlap
